The upgrade task will fail with an exception if the results directory doesn't exist.

The workaround is to manually add the results directory. So if the upgrade failed for plan {{JRA-DEF}}, then add the directory:

{{BAMBOO_HOME/xml-data/builds/JRA-DEF/results}}

